        || '||' || COALESCE(annual_statement_line,'NULL')) as msgr_part_three_key,
        msgr_last_update_date 
    from dbo.msgrmissinglossrevenue
) f
left outer join (
    select
        i.policy_key as "master policy key",
        i.agency_code,
        i.company_desc as "company desc",
        i.formatted_policy_number as "policy number",
        i.policy_number,
        c.display_renewalcd as "renewal code desc",
        i.fairplan_desc as "fairplan desc",
        r.lob_display_group_desc as "lob group desc",
        i.new_renewal_desc as "new renewal desc",
        r.lob_display_desc as "lob desc",
        i.insurance_score_desc as "insurance score desc",
        i.secondary_home_desc as "secondary home desc",
        i.policy_inception_date as "policy inception date",
        i.policy_effective_date as "policy effective date",
        i.policy_expiration_date as "policy expiration date",
        i.policy_symbol as "policy symbol",
        i.formatted_module_number as "module number",
        i.insurance_score,
        i.new_business_entry_date as "policy transaction dt",
        s.insured_name as "insured name",
        i.insurance_score_2,
        i.insurance_score_desc_2,
        i.producer_code as "producer code",
        i.blanket_policy_ind as "blanket policy ind",
        i.billingtype as "billing type",
        s.insured_address1,
        s.insured_address2,
        s.insured_city,
        s.insured_zip,
        s.formattedinsuredaddress as "formatted insured address",
        i.insurance_score_year,
        i.insurance_score_2_year,
        CASE WHEN i.msgr_last_update_date < s.last_upd_dt THEN i.msgr_last_update_date ELSE s.last_upd_dt END AS msgr_last_update_date 
    from (
        select
            agency_code,
            billingtype,
            blanket_policy_ind,
            company_desc,
            fairplan_desc,
            formatted_module_number,
            formatted_policy_number,
            insurance_score,
            insurance_score_desc,
            insurance_score_2,
            insurance_score_desc_2,
            lob_desc,
            new_business_entry_date,
            new_renewal_desc,
            policy_effective_date,
            policy_expiration_date,
            policy_inception_date,
            policy_renewal_code,
            policy_key,
            policy_symbol,
            producer_code,
            secondary_home_desc,
            policy_number,
            insurance_score_year,
            insurance_score_2_year,
            msgr_last_update_date 
        from dbo.msgr_pms_master_policy
    ) i
    left outer join (
        select
            formattedinsuredaddress,
            insured_address1,
            insured_address2,
            insured_city,
            insured_name,
            insured_zip,
            policy_key,
            last_upd_dt
        from dbo.pms_master_insured
    ) s on s.policy_key = i.policy_key
    left outer join (
        select
            lob_display_desc,
            lob_display_group_desc,
            pms_lob_desc
        from dbo.lob_ref
    ) r on r.pms_lob_desc = i.lob_desc
    left outer join (
        select
            display_renewalcd,
            pmsrenewalcd
        from dbo.renewalcode_ref
    ) c on c.pmsrenewalcd = i.policy_renewal_code
) p on p."master policy key" = f."policy key"
left outer join (
    select
        "agency address",
        "agency alpha workflow",
        "agency appointed dt",
        "agency city",
        "agency city state",
		CASE
            WHEN LEN(dbo.msgr_view_master_agency."agency code") < 4
            THEN LPAD(msgr_view_master_agency."agency code",4,'0')
            ELSE dbo.msgr_view_master_agency."agency code"
        END as "agency code",
        "agency contact phone",
        "agency group",
		"agency id",
        "agency name",
        "agency state",
        "agency zip code",
        "field representative",
        "field representative group",
        "group name",
        msgr_last_update_date
    from dbo.msgr_view_master_agency
    where "field representative" != 'Jim Ford'
) a on a."agency code" = p.agency_code
left outer join (
    select
        cat_desc,
        cat_group_desc,
        claim_key,
        claim_number,
        claim_status,
        last_upd_dt
    from dbo.pms_master_claim
) c on c.claim_key = f."claim key"
left outer join (
    select
        claim_status,
        claim_status_display_value
    from dbo.claimstatus_ref
) cs on c.claim_status = cs.claim_status
left outer join (
    select
        dim_desc,
        dim_id
    from dbo.hier_dim_majorperil
) m on m.dim_id = f."major peril id"
left outer join (
    select
        dim_desc,
        dim_id,
        gen4_desc
    from dbo.hier_dim_riskstate
) s on s.dim_id = f."risk state id"
left outer join (
    select
        building_limits_group as "building limits group",
        building_limits as "building limits",
        building_class_code as "building class",
        contents_class_code as "contents class",
        display_constructiontype as "construction type",
        construction_year as "construction year",
        construction_year_band as "construction year band",
        contents_limits as "contents limits",
        deductible,
        liability_limit as "liability limit",
        number_of_apartments as "number of apartments",
        number_of_families as "number of families",
        display_occupancydesc as "occupancy",
        policy_key_code,
        protection_class as "protection class",
        sprinkler_indicator as "sprinkler",
        form,
        rating_territory as "rating territory",
        rating_territory_desc as "rating territory desc",
        building_amount as "building limit amt",
        individual_risk_premium_mod,
        age_credit,
        dupc,
        prc,
        expense_mod,
        latitude,
        longitude,
        total_insured_value as "total insured value",
        risk_address_line_1,
        risk_address_line_2,
        risk_address_line_3,
        risk_city as "risk city",
        risk_postal_cd as "risk zip",
        coverage_a_premium,
        coverage_c_premium,
        water_backup_limit,
        personal_umbrella_limit as "personal umbrella limit",
        commercial_umbrella_liability_limit as "commercial umbrella liability limit",
        commercial_excess_liability_limit as "commercial excess liability limit",
        building_limit_band_1k as "building limit band 1k",
        building_limit_band_100k as "building limit band 100k",
        building_limit_band_500k as "building limit band 500k",
        contents_amount as "contents limit",
        number_of_apartments_band as "number of apartments band",
        number_of_stories as "number of stories",
        number_of_stories_band as "number of stories band",
        sq_feet_area as "sq feet area",
        num_vehicles as "num vehicles",
        building_class_description as "building class description",
        contents_class_description as "contents class description",
        sir_result_feet,
        sir_mile,
        distance_to_shoreband,
        sir_coastline_band,
        distance_to_coast_feet,
        distance_to_coast_mile,
        flood,
        elevation,
        risk_count as "num buildings complex",
        sqft_area_band as "sq feet area band",
        formattedriskaddress as "formatted risk address",
        formattedriskcity as "formatted risk city",
        formattedriskzipcode as "formatted risk zip",
        formattedlatitude as "formatted risk latitude",
        formattedlongitude as "formatted risk longitude",
        formattedstreet,
        formattedcounty,
        wind_site_deductible,
        per_unit_deductible_amt,
        per_unit_deductible_type,
        msgr_last_update_date 
    from dbo.msgr_pms_master_risk
) r on r.policy_key_code = f."policy key code"
left join (
    select
        policy_number,
        cast(max(inspection_dt) as datetime) inspectiondt
    from dbo.pms_inspection
    group by policy_number
) ad on p.policy_number = ad.policy_number
 left join dbo.msgr_part_three TGT
 on f.msgr_part_three_key = TGT.msgr_part_three_key
 WHERE (f.msgr_last_update_date >= dateadd('day', -1, date_trunc('day', getdate()))
 --(SELECT etlbatchstartst FROM dbo.loadbatchetldt WHERE loadetltype = 'wf_msgr_part1_part2_part3')
 OR p.msgr_last_update_date >= dateadd('day', -1, date_trunc('day', getdate()))
 --(SELECT etlbatchstartst FROM dbo.loadbatchetldt WHERE loadetltype = 'wf_msgr_part1_part2_part3')
 OR a.msgr_last_update_date >= dateadd('day', -1, date_trunc('day', getdate()))
 --(SELECT etlbatchstartst FROM dbo.loadbatchetldt WHERE loadetltype = 'wf_msgr_part1_part2_part3')
 OR c.last_upd_dt >= (SELECT etlbatchstartst FROM dbo.loadbatchetldt WHERE loadetltype = 'wf_msgr_part1_part2_part3')
 OR r.msgr_last_update_date >= dateadd('day', -1, date_trunc('day', getdate()))
 --(SELECT etlbatchstartst FROM dbo.loadbatchetldt WHERE loadetltype = 'wf_msgr_part1_part2_part3')
 )

fields.name: Policy_Key_Code_Flag
fields.expression:
--CASE 
--		WHEN RIGHT(F.[Policy Key Code], 4) = '-999'
--			OR (
--				LEFT(F.[Policy Key Code], 3) = 'SBP'
--				AND RIGHT(F.[Policy Key Code], 4) = '-000'
--				)
--			THEN 0
--		ELSE 1
--		END AS [Policy Key Code Flag]

IIF(SUBSTR(policy_key_code1, -4, 4) = '-999'
OR (SUBSTR(policy_key_code1, 1, 3) = 'SBP' AND SUBSTR(policy_key_code1, -4, 4) = '-000'), 0, 1)

--CONCAT (
--			LTRIM(RTRIM(S.Insured_Address1))
